PART I — THE SOVEREIGN THESIS
──────────────────────────────

The global property management market is a $4.2T fragmented chaos.
120 jurisdictions. Zero interoperability. Legacy SaaS born in 2005.

easyTenancy is not a product. It is a Sovereign Economic OS.

A distributed intelligence layer that converts raw property data into
autonomous revenue — perpetually, globally, without human bottlenecks.

The goal is not market share. The goal is market definition.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

