PART III — THE AUTONOMOUS REVENUE ENGINE
──────────────────────────────────────────

5-stage pipeline. Zero human intervention required for standard renewals.

  DETECT ──→ DRAFT ──→ STAGE ──→ SIGN ──→ CAPTURE
     │           │         │         │         │
  Einstein    Gemini    Novita    WebAuthn  MetricsTicker
  Score≥75   2.5 Pro  FLUX.1 AR  FIDO2     +$2.5% fee

Stage Details:

  1. DETECT  ActionableIntelligence monitors Einstein scores every 60s.
             Any tenant with score ≥ 75 triggers CHURN_DETECTED event.
             Agentforce Autonomous Negotiator is instantiated.
             Target: <2s detection latency globally via CF D1 edge.

  2. DRAFT   AICopilot receives AGENTFORCE_TRIGGER via Orchestrator bus.
             Gemini 2.5 Pro (high-value) or 2.0 Flash (standard) drafts
             a market-adjusted lease renewal proposal in <8s.
             ROICalculator auto-generates 2026 market comps in parallel.

  3. STAGE   SpatialStaging triggers Novita GPU pipeline.
             FLUX.1-dev generates photorealistic AR walkthrough assets.
             RadialMap enables WebXR "Teleportation Mode" transition
             from 2D portfolio view → 3D immersive property tour.
             Target: <45s render time for SDXL assets.

  4. SIGN    WebAuthnLogin gates the proposal with FIDO2 biometrics.
             Touch ID / Face ID / Windows Hello — no passwords.
             Turnstile bot-protection ensures only humans can sign.
             Smart contract signature logged with CF timestamp proof.

  5. CAPTURE MetricsTicker logs SUCCESS_FEE_CAPTURED event.
             2.5% success fee auto-invoiced via Salesforce Revenue Cloud.
             HeroStateWidget updated with live portfolio metrics.
             ARR growth curve advances toward $1.345B target.

