PART V — SOVEREIGN SECURITY DOCTRINE
───────────────────────────────────────

Layer 1 — Network (Cloudflare):
  • 300+ PoPs · Argo Smart Routing · Smart Placement
  • TLS 1.3 + X25519Kyber768 (Post-Quantum KEM, active now)
  • DDoS mitigation: 321 Tbps network capacity
  • Bot Management: ML-based fingerprinting (Turnstile invisible)

Layer 2 — Application (WebAuthn FIDO2):
  • Passkeys replace passwords on all /app/* routes
  • FIDO2 credentials: Touch ID, Face ID, Windows Hello, YubiKey
  • No passwords transmitted or stored — ever
  • Replay attack protection: challenge-response nonce per session

Layer 3 — Data (Cloudflare D1 + PQ roadmap):
  • D1 SQLite: globally distributed, sub-15ms reads at edge
  • KV: session tokens, compliance cache, rate limiting
  • R2: AR walkthrough assets, lease document storage
  • PQ Roadmap: ES256 → ML-DSA-65 (FIPS 204) by 2027-Q1

Layer 4 — Compliance (ComplianceEngine):
  • IP Intelligence → jurisdiction detection (CF-IPCountry header)
  • GDPR: DPA automation, Article 22 AI disclosure, cookie consent
  • CCPA: DNSMI opt-out, 45-day DSRP response pipeline
  • KES: ODPC registration, iTax API, M-Pesa audit trail
  • PDPA/POPIA: purpose limitation, Information Officer workflow

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

PART VI — GLOBAL DEPLOYMENT ARCHITECTURE
──────────────────────────────────────────

  Cloudflare Pages (edge CDN, 300+ PoPs)
    └── React SPA (Vite + Hono + framer-motion)
        └── GlobalOrchestrator.ts (pub/sub event bus)
            ├── ActionableIntelligence  ← Salesforce Agentforce
            ├── AICopilot               ← Gemini 2.5 Pro / 2.0 Flash
            ├── AIFeed                  ← Real-time Cloudflare KV stream
            ├── CompliancePanel         ← ComplianceEngine.ts rules
            ├── FeatureMicroTours       ← Onboarding orchestration
            ├── HeroStateWidget         ← Live portfolio snapshot
            ├── MetricsTicker           ← Value-Capture Engine ($1.345B)
            ├── Nav                     ← Route-aware navigation
            ├── RadialMap               ← D3 force + WebXR portal
            ├── ROICalculator           ← 2026 market-adjusted proposals
            ├── SpatialStaging          ← Novita FLUX.1 AR pipeline
            ├── TurnstileWidget         ← CF bot protection
            ├── WebAuthnLogin           ← FIDO2 biometric gate
            └── Logo                    ← Brand identity anchor

  Cloudflare D1 (edge SQLite):
    • tenants, leases, compliance_log, fee_events, ar_renders

  Cloudflare KV (edge K/V):
    • session tokens, jurisdiction cache, turnstile replay protection

  Cloudflare R2 (object storage):
    • AR walkthrough assets, lease documents, compliance certificates

  API Routes (server.mjs / functions/):
    • /api/ai/chat          → Gemini proxy (model selection logic)
    • /api/ai/retention-email → Agentforce retention workflow
    • /api/turnstile/verify → CF Turnstile server-side validation
    • /api/orchestrator/events → SSE stream for real-time Orchestrator sync
    • /api/compliance/jurisdiction → IP→regime detection
    • /api/metrics/live     → Live KPI JSON endpoint
    • /api/og               → Branded SVG OG image generation

